December 31</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../624/34624.xml">
1945</link>) is an Australian film and television <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../753/753.xml">
actor</link> who has built his career around action-type films, most often cast as a villain. He began appearing on Australian television shows in the mid-1970s, such as <it><series wordnetid="108457976" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
