<p>

He is best known to international audiences for his role of "Wez", in the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../776/34776.xml">
1981</link> science fiction action film . After <it>Mad Max 2</it>, Wells began appearing in Hollywood films, such as the military action film <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../483/230483.xml">
Commando</link></movie>
</it> (<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../846/34846.xml">
1985</link>), which starred <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<manufacturer wordnetid="110292316" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
