<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../806/1806.xml">
Arnold Schwarzenegger</link></actor>
</governor>
</bodybuilder>
</manufacturer>
</person>
 in <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../483/230483.xml">
Commando</link></movie>
</it> (<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../846/34846.xml">
1985</link>). When first approached for the role in <it>Commando</it>, Wells was in Australia working on the feature film, <it>Fortress</it> based on the real life <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
<child wordnetid="109917593" confidence="0.8">
<person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.8">
<transgression wordnetid="100745005" confidence="0.8">
<event wordnetid="100029378" confidence="0.8">
